WEBVTT

00:01:03.840 --> 00:01:05.360
Good evening, ladies and gentlemen.

00:01:06.140 --> 00:01:07.980
I request Mr. Patnaik to come and make the opening remarks.

00:01:07.980 --> 00:01:08.920


00:01:19.440 --> 00:01:27.600
Her Holiness, Shri Mataji, Sir C.P.,

00:01:27.600 --> 00:01:37.020
Honorable Cabinet Secretary, Mrs. Kumar, Mrs. Ghosh,

00:01:37.020 --> 00:01:45.020
my seniors, colleagues, friends, and all members of

00:01:45.020 --> 00:01:51.980
my Sahaja Yoga family, we have gathered here today

00:01:51.980 --> 00:02:03.040
to get the blessings from Shri Mataji,

00:02:03.040 --> 00:02:07.020
who will show us the way to fight

00:02:07.020 --> 00:02:10.440
the stress and tension that is prevailing in our life.

00:02:10.440 --> 00:02:10.780


00:02:14.170 --> 00:02:16.210
This is a unique program.

00:02:17.450 --> 00:02:20.930
Earlier, Shri Mataji had a similar program

00:02:20.930 --> 00:02:27.650
in Bombay and it was very much appreciated and

00:02:27.650 --> 00:02:31.970
it was very useful for bureaucrats like us.

00:02:34.190 --> 00:02:36.750
We are now living in the era

00:02:36.750 --> 00:02:41.290
of knowledge, where speed is the essence of life.

00:02:42.930 --> 00:02:45.730
The Darwinian theory of survival of the fittest

00:02:45.730 --> 00:02:49.590
was never so true as it is today.

00:02:50.350 --> 00:02:54.810
We have to continuously run to remain where we are.

00:02:54.810 --> 00:02:55.310


00:02:58.110 --> 00:03:03.910
That creates friction, pressure and tension in our life.

00:03:03.910 --> 00:03:04.210


00:03:06.390 --> 00:03:08.910
Shri Mataji, in Her beautiful words, will tell you

00:03:08.910 --> 00:03:14.930
how the subtle inner system gets affected

00:03:14.930 --> 00:03:20.010
by the chaotic outer world and how

00:03:20.010 --> 00:03:24.610
it affects our health, our walking and our general view towards life.

00:03:24.610 --> 00:03:25.590


00:03:29.390 --> 00:03:37.090
We know cases of senior bureaucrats in their

00:03:37.090 --> 00:03:43.450
forties getting heart attack and succumbing to it.

00:03:43.710 --> 00:03:47.490
It has happened in Delhi itself and elsewhere in the country.

00:03:47.490 --> 00:03:48.150


00:03:50.810 --> 00:03:58.150
Whether it is the job itself, interference from

00:03:58.150 --> 00:04:03.610
outside, transfer, posting, it can be anything besides

00:04:03.610 --> 00:04:05.450
the usual tensions of life.

00:04:07.110 --> 00:04:12.470
We are fortunate to have amongst us

00:04:12.470 --> 00:04:15.970
Sir C.P. who has been a career bureaucrat

00:04:15.970 --> 00:04:20.950
like us and has seen both the worlds,

00:04:21.650 --> 00:04:23.850
the world of a bureaucrat and

00:04:23.850 --> 00:04:25.450
the world of Sahaja Yoga.

00:04:26.830 --> 00:04:31.530
Who can be more suited to address us

00:04:31.530 --> 00:04:38.250
than Sir C.P.? Of course, Her Holiness

00:04:38.250 --> 00:04:40.230
Mataji is amongst us.

00:04:41.370 --> 00:04:44.970
She will tell us in detail how

00:04:44.970 --> 00:04:51.770
Sahaja Yoga will help us in facing the tension

00:04:51.770 --> 00:04:53.830
and pressures in our career.

00:04:55.330 --> 00:04:56.890
I will not take much of your time.

00:04:57.810 --> 00:05:01.650
Now I request Mrs. Ghosh, who is the

00:05:01.650 --> 00:05:07.490
General Secretary of IAS Wives Association

00:05:07.490 --> 00:05:11.430
to come here and continue the proceedings.

00:05:18.620 --> 00:05:21.060
Good evening ladies and gentlemen.

00:05:21.800 --> 00:05:25.980
I request the President of our Association,

00:05:26.040 --> 00:05:29.800
Mrs. Pratima Kumar to present garlands and flowers

00:05:29.800 --> 00:05:34.500
to Her Holiness Shri Mataji Shri Nirmal Devi and

00:05:34.500 --> 00:05:36.740
flowers to Sir C.P. Srivastava.

00:06:15.830 --> 00:06:20.570
Mrs. Rama Patnaik will now present flowers to

00:06:20.570 --> 00:06:41.750
the office bearers of the IAS Wives Association.

00:06:41.750 --> 00:06:42.290


00:07:04.530 --> 00:07:08.370
Our IASOA, that is the Indian Administrative Service

00:07:08.370 --> 00:07:12.830
Officers Wives Association, is a welfare organization

00:07:12.830 --> 00:07:16.710
set up mainly to promote welfare activities and

00:07:16.710 --> 00:07:19.410
to be a forum for discussion of topical issues.

00:07:20.190 --> 00:07:22.770
We do try to cater to a wide range

00:07:22.770 --> 00:07:26.370
of interests among our members to arrange

00:07:26.370 --> 00:07:31.570
talks and demonstrations and encourage social work.

00:07:32.390 --> 00:07:34.790
Many of you must be knowing about the

00:07:34.790 --> 00:07:38.130
Sanskriti school run by the Civil Services Society

00:07:38.130 --> 00:07:39.950
with which we are associated.

00:07:40.490 --> 00:07:43.150
We hope to do much more by way of social work.

00:07:43.150 --> 00:07:44.090


00:07:45.530 --> 00:07:47.570
That was briefly about our association.

00:07:48.170 --> 00:07:51.890
Now to come to the event of this evening.

00:07:51.890 --> 00:07:52.250


00:07:53.330 --> 00:07:58.270
Her Holiness Mataji Shri Nirmala Devi was born

00:07:58.270 --> 00:08:03.310
on 21st March 1923 at Chindwara, Madhya Pradesh.

00:08:03.970 --> 00:08:06.030
She is the daughter of late Shri P.K. Salve,

00:08:06.030 --> 00:08:08.850
who was a great freedom fighter.

00:08:09.210 --> 00:08:11.930
He was a member of the Constituent Assembly

00:08:11.930 --> 00:08:14.190
and the Mayor of Nagpur.

00:08:14.950 --> 00:08:18.110
Her mother was a mathematics scholar and

00:08:18.110 --> 00:08:19.230
a freedom fighter too.

00:08:20.010 --> 00:08:21.710
She is the wife of Sir C.P.

00:08:21.790 --> 00:08:25.230
Srivastava, a member of the Indian Administrative Service

00:08:25.230 --> 00:08:27.530
about whom I will be speaking in detail later.

00:08:27.530 --> 00:08:27.890


00:08:28.790 --> 00:08:32.390
Her Holiness Mataji Shri Nirmala Devi has been

00:08:32.390 --> 00:08:36.450
a spiritual personality since birth and has inherited

00:08:36.450 --> 00:08:38.289
patriotism from her family.

00:08:38.929 --> 00:08:42.169
She studied in a medical college and participated

00:08:42.169 --> 00:08:43.670
in the freedom movement.

00:08:44.710 --> 00:08:47.930
She worked with Mahatma Gandhi in his ashram

00:08:47.930 --> 00:08:49.110
in Her childhood.

00:08:50.130 --> 00:08:53.650
The late Shri Lal Bahadur Shastri recognized

00:08:53.650 --> 00:08:57.650
Shri Mataji and sought Her advice many times when

00:08:57.650 --> 00:09:00.450
Sir C.P. Srivastava was secretary to the

00:09:00.450 --> 00:09:02.190
late Shri Shastri.

00:09:02.810 --> 00:09:06.790
For the last 29 years, Shri Mataji has been

00:09:06.790 --> 00:09:12.270
working relentlessly for the emancipation, upliftment and

00:09:12.270 --> 00:09:14.870
benefit of the entire human community.

00:09:15.570 --> 00:09:18.810
Shri Mataji has been doing basic and fundamental

00:09:18.810 --> 00:09:23.770
work of spirituality by awakening Kundalini power in

00:09:23.770 --> 00:09:29.310
human beings and Sahastrara individually and also en masse

00:09:29.310 --> 00:09:34.550
and thus improving one's physical, mental, emotional and

00:09:34.550 --> 00:09:40.150
spiritual situation and simultaneously the improvement reflects

00:09:40.150 --> 00:09:42.830
at the collective level of our society and the nation.

00:09:42.830 --> 00:09:43.330


00:09:44.330 --> 00:09:47.490
Shri Mataji will be addressing us in detail

00:09:47.490 --> 00:09:52.830
about Sahaja Yoga and specifically about stress

00:09:52.830 --> 00:09:55.350
and tension management through Sahaja Yoga.

00:09:56.430 --> 00:09:59.830
She has started various hospitals and schools based

00:09:59.830 --> 00:10:03.930
on Sahaj methods which includes Sahaj Hospital at

00:10:03.930 --> 00:10:07.710
Vashi, Mumbai where thousands of patients of chronic

00:10:07.710 --> 00:10:11.310
diseases have been cured and schools at Dharamshala,

00:10:11.670 --> 00:10:13.910
Himachal Pradesh and in Rome.

00:10:14.670 --> 00:10:18.030
She has founded a music academy in Nagpur

00:10:18.030 --> 00:10:22.170
for teaching Indian classical music, dance and art.

00:10:22.790 --> 00:10:25.510
She has also started a home for destitute

00:10:25.510 --> 00:10:29.190
women and street urchins and an NGO

00:10:29.190 --> 00:10:31.730
to rehabilitate them in Noida, Uttar Pradesh.

00:10:32.850 --> 00:10:36.930
Shri Mataji has been recognized worldwide by several

00:10:36.930 --> 00:10:41.410
countries and prestigious institutions for Her selfless work

00:10:41.410 --> 00:10:44.610
and for the powerful results of Her spiritual teachings.

00:10:44.610 --> 00:10:45.210


00:10:46.530 --> 00:10:49.050
Due to paucity of time, I will mention only a few.

00:10:49.050 --> 00:10:50.050


00:10:50.810 --> 00:10:55.070
In 1992, She was appointed honorary member of

00:10:55.070 --> 00:10:59.270
the Presidium of Petrovskaya Academy of Art and

00:10:59.270 --> 00:11:04.390
Science in Russia, Einstein being the recipient

00:11:04.390 --> 00:11:05.810
of such an honor in the past.

00:11:06.590 --> 00:11:12.110
In 1995, the Romanian Ecological University awarded

00:11:12.110 --> 00:11:15.390
a degree of doctorate in Cognitive Sciences to Her

00:11:15.390 --> 00:11:18.290
and the same year She was invited to

00:11:18.290 --> 00:11:21.710
speak at the International Women's Conference in Beijing.

00:11:22.770 --> 00:11:25.310
Her name was proposed as a candidate for

00:11:25.310 --> 00:11:27.830
the Nobel Peace Prize in 1996.

00:11:28.990 --> 00:11:33.790
In 1997, Her humanitarian work was recognized in

00:11:33.790 --> 00:11:36.850
a proclamation by the United States of America

00:11:36.850 --> 00:11:40.530
Congress which was submitted to the Congressional Records.

00:11:42.510 --> 00:11:46.270
Sir C.P. Srivastava was born in 1920

00:11:46.270 --> 00:11:48.290
in Uttar Pradesh.

00:11:49.090 --> 00:11:51.750
He was married to Shri Mataji in 1947 in Delhi.

00:11:51.750 --> 00:11:52.730


00:11:53.590 --> 00:11:57.250
He belongs to the 1947 batch of the IAS

00:11:57.250 --> 00:12:01.890
and besides several other posts, he worked

00:12:01.890 --> 00:12:05.110
as secretary to the Prime Minister late Shri Lal Bahadur Shastri.

00:12:05.110 --> 00:12:06.370


00:12:06.870 --> 00:12:10.170
He also worked as chairman cum managing director

00:12:10.170 --> 00:12:13.450
of the Shipping Corporation of India and

00:12:13.450 --> 00:12:17.610
was elected for four consecutive terms that is

00:12:17.610 --> 00:12:20.130
16 years to be the secretary general of the

00:12:20.130 --> 00:12:23.370
United Nations International Maritime Organization.

00:12:24.250 --> 00:12:26.790
He is the founder chancellor of the World

00:12:26.790 --> 00:12:28.730
Maritime University Sweden.

00:12:29.510 --> 00:12:32.910
Among various awards and honors, Sir C.P.

00:12:32.970 --> 00:12:36.590
Srivastava was awarded the Padma Bhushan in 1972.

00:12:38.410 --> 00:12:42.190
He received decorations from more than 30 nations.

00:12:42.650 --> 00:12:47.010
One of these distinguished decorations includes the knighthood

00:12:47.010 --> 00:12:49.590
of the highest order from the Queen

00:12:49.590 --> 00:12:52.850
of England, the first Indian to receive such

00:12:52.850 --> 00:12:55.070
an award after India's independence.

00:12:55.950 --> 00:12:57.970
He is the author of a book on

00:12:57.970 --> 00:13:01.310
the late Shri Lal Bahadur Shastri titled

00:13:01.310 --> 00:13:03.070
A Life of Truth in Politics.

00:13:03.770 --> 00:13:06.910
Another of his books on corruption is currently under print.

00:13:06.910 --> 00:13:07.790


00:13:09.810 --> 00:13:14.110
I now request Sir C.P. Srivastava to address the gathering.

00:13:14.110 --> 00:13:15.350


00:13:33.900 --> 00:13:40.240
Madam President, Distinguished Cabinet Secretary Shri Prabhat Kumarji,

00:13:41.500 --> 00:13:46.760
Distinguished Ladies on the dais, Distinguished Ladies

00:13:46.760 --> 00:13:50.680
and Gentlemen, It is a great honor to be

00:13:50.680 --> 00:13:52.720
asked to say a few words on this

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:54.880
very unique occasion.

00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:58.540
And I am most grateful to you,

00:13:58.540 --> 00:14:00.460
ma'am, for the very kind words in which

00:14:00.460 --> 00:14:02.060
you have introduced me.

00:14:04.660 --> 00:14:08.380
To talk about Sahaja Yoga, I must first

00:14:08.380 --> 00:14:11.240
tell you how I got into it, for that

00:14:11.240 --> 00:14:12.580
I think would be of interest

00:14:12.580 --> 00:14:13.880
to some of you in any case.

00:14:15.820 --> 00:14:18.300
As has been mentioned already, we got married

00:14:18.300 --> 00:14:23.640
53 years ago, and we completed 53 years yesterday.

00:14:23.640 --> 00:14:24.260


00:14:24.520 --> 00:14:26.120
Today we are beginning 54th.

00:14:26.940 --> 00:14:31.340
Now during this time for 29 years,

00:14:31.340 --> 00:14:36.560
we have been dealing with Sahaja Yoga and various

00:14:36.560 --> 00:14:37.700
aspects in our own way.

00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:41.540
When we got married, I made a very good bargain.

00:14:41.540 --> 00:14:42.060


00:14:43.200 --> 00:14:45.200
I told my wife, I said, I'll only

00:14:45.200 --> 00:14:47.840
deal with official matters, the rest is all yours.

00:14:47.840 --> 00:14:48.180


00:14:49.340 --> 00:14:54.320
Children, any, family, household, that's all yours.

00:14:54.760 --> 00:14:57.560
Any transfers we manage, I'll only deal with my official work.

00:14:57.560 --> 00:14:58.380


00:14:58.880 --> 00:15:01.380
And She maintained that throughout our life.

00:15:01.540 --> 00:15:03.920
In other words, I have absolutely nothing

00:15:03.920 --> 00:15:06.020
to do with the upbringing of our children or

00:15:06.020 --> 00:15:08.840
running the family or any household affairs.

00:15:10.200 --> 00:15:12.340
Now, that moment, I could be very busy with my work.

00:15:12.340 --> 00:15:13.280


00:15:15.660 --> 00:15:18.120
A development took place in 1970.

00:15:19.200 --> 00:15:22.600
Until then, She was devoting Herself to the family responsibilities.

00:15:22.600 --> 00:15:23.580


00:15:24.460 --> 00:15:27.380
But in 1970, sometime in the month of May,

00:15:27.380 --> 00:15:30.800
She one day told me, rather somberly,

00:15:31.000 --> 00:15:34.360
She said She had decided to devote Her

00:15:34.360 --> 00:15:36.440
time now to Sahaja Yoga.

00:15:37.540 --> 00:15:38.760
So I asked what was that?

00:15:39.500 --> 00:15:43.160
And She explained that She wanted to assist

00:15:43.160 --> 00:15:48.440
men and women to have a unique spiritual

00:15:48.440 --> 00:15:52.440
experience through which they could get transformed and

00:15:52.440 --> 00:15:58.280
become really good, chaste, moral, honest human beings.

00:16:00.180 --> 00:16:02.020
I asked, do You really believe that You can do so?

00:16:02.020 --> 00:16:02.640


00:16:03.300 --> 00:16:05.780
She said yes, She can help men and

00:16:05.780 --> 00:16:08.160
women to raise their Kundalini, which is their power.

00:16:08.160 --> 00:16:08.520


00:16:09.360 --> 00:16:11.400
And then the result follows.

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:15.960
I assure you, ladies and gentlemen, to use

00:16:15.960 --> 00:16:18.220
an American cliche, I didn't quite buy that.

00:16:19.280 --> 00:16:22.680
I said, are You sure You can do that?

00:16:22.680 --> 00:16:23.000


00:16:23.520 --> 00:16:26.180
Because I had dealt with many, many persons

00:16:26.180 --> 00:16:28.020
during my career, and I don't think I

00:16:28.020 --> 00:16:29.860
can say that I was able to transform

00:16:29.860 --> 00:16:30.880
even a single person.

00:16:32.060 --> 00:16:34.280
How could She do all this?

00:16:34.860 --> 00:16:37.420
I didn't quite understand what She meant.

00:16:37.800 --> 00:16:39.860
Anyway, I said, of course, if you want

00:16:39.860 --> 00:16:41.160
to do it, by all means.

00:16:41.780 --> 00:16:43.160
But the point I want to make now

00:16:43.160 --> 00:16:45.780
is that She began to devote herself to

00:16:45.780 --> 00:16:51.080
Sahaja Yoga without in any way diluting Her

00:16:51.080 --> 00:16:53.060
responsibilities to the family.

00:16:54.020 --> 00:16:56.560
That was something additional that She was doing.

00:16:57.080 --> 00:17:00.120
She started to address small groups first,

00:17:00.120 --> 00:17:02.480
and then larger groups, and things developed.

00:17:03.000 --> 00:17:04.599
But as far as I was concerned, being

00:17:04.599 --> 00:17:06.859
a civil servant, a bureaucrat, trained not to

00:17:06.859 --> 00:17:09.520
accept anything until it's proved three times over,

00:17:09.520 --> 00:17:11.079
I was still very skeptical.

00:17:12.359 --> 00:17:15.560
So I kept watching from a distance, aloof,

00:17:16.619 --> 00:17:17.640
and things went on.

00:17:18.800 --> 00:17:21.200
And then a new development took place, which

00:17:21.200 --> 00:17:23.000
changed me also.

00:17:24.079 --> 00:17:26.720
In 1973, I was elected, as has been

00:17:26.720 --> 00:17:29.220
mentioned, as Secretary General of the United Nations

00:17:29.220 --> 00:17:31.220
International Maritime Organization.

00:17:32.040 --> 00:17:35.640
We went to London and took up residence

00:17:35.640 --> 00:17:37.680
in Surrey, just outside London.

00:17:37.680 --> 00:17:41.260
There was a house, lovely house, and

00:17:41.260 --> 00:17:44.360
my wife, we had some domestics also, were living there.

00:17:44.360 --> 00:17:44.680


00:17:45.740 --> 00:17:48.280
Then the day came when something was to happen.

00:17:48.280 --> 00:17:48.560


00:17:49.760 --> 00:17:52.180
One day I returned late in the evening.

00:17:53.980 --> 00:17:56.040
My cook opened the door, let me in,

00:17:56.520 --> 00:17:58.720
and I went to the drawing room of

00:17:58.720 --> 00:18:00.960
the house, where normally my wife would be waiting for me.

00:18:00.960 --> 00:18:01.620


00:18:02.160 --> 00:18:05.460
But instead of Her, there I saw

00:18:05.460 --> 00:18:08.780
a young man, white-skinned, sitting on the sofa and reading newspaper.

00:18:08.780 --> 00:18:09.760


00:18:11.380 --> 00:18:14.660
And I wondered whether there was something wrong,

00:18:14.760 --> 00:18:16.480
because I had no information that any guest was to arrive.

00:18:16.480 --> 00:18:17.080


00:18:18.080 --> 00:18:21.680
But anyway, I waited for a moment and

00:18:21.680 --> 00:18:25.000
looked at him again, and found that

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:26.740
he was not only sitting there, he was very

00:18:26.740 --> 00:18:29.580
much there, but he was wearing my own

00:18:29.580 --> 00:18:31.260
clothes, my kurta and pyjama.

00:18:32.200 --> 00:18:34.140
So I said, well, there's something seriously wrong with me.

00:18:34.140 --> 00:18:34.600


00:18:35.140 --> 00:18:37.080
I must check.

00:18:37.560 --> 00:18:40.120
So I receded, went to the kitchen, where

00:18:40.120 --> 00:18:41.920
my wife was giving instructions to the cook,

00:18:42.400 --> 00:18:44.440
and said, please tell me, do I see what I see?

00:18:44.440 --> 00:18:45.040


00:18:45.720 --> 00:18:47.340
So She said, yes, very much.

00:18:47.460 --> 00:18:49.080
And then She explained to me, She said,

00:18:49.120 --> 00:18:49.840
you know what happened?

00:18:50.980 --> 00:18:53.500
She had gone that day to London to

00:18:53.500 --> 00:18:56.020
Piccadilly Circus, and there She saw a young

00:18:56.020 --> 00:19:01.060
man lying, uncared for, obviously very sick, near the fountain.

00:19:01.060 --> 00:19:01.700


00:19:02.460 --> 00:19:05.360
So She, She's a very compassionate person, I've

00:19:05.360 --> 00:19:06.680
known that ever since.

00:19:07.180 --> 00:19:10.000
She went over and asked what the matter was.

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:10.400


00:19:11.120 --> 00:19:13.260
And this boy said he didn't have anyone

00:19:13.260 --> 00:19:14.900
to look after him, he was living rough,

00:19:14.980 --> 00:19:17.540
as they say in London, and he was

00:19:17.540 --> 00:19:20.740
very sick, jaundice, drugs, and so on.

00:19:21.860 --> 00:19:23.880
Now, only She could have done what She did.

00:19:23.880 --> 00:19:24.120


00:19:24.300 --> 00:19:26.800
She said, okay, if no one to look

00:19:26.800 --> 00:19:28.920
after you, come along, come with Me, hop

00:19:28.920 --> 00:19:30.300
into My car, I'll take you home.

00:19:31.200 --> 00:19:32.680
And so She brought him home.

00:19:33.840 --> 00:19:35.940
