00:38:40.590 --> 00:38:42.490
So this is the Gyana Marga we are

00:38:42.490 --> 00:38:44.890
talking about of the Absolute knowledge.

00:38:45.470 --> 00:38:48.850
Now this torsion area is a wonderful thing

00:38:48.850 --> 00:38:53.910
because this Kundalini, when She rises, She not

00:38:53.910 --> 00:38:57.650
