00:48:38.950 --> 00:48:45.350
it's all nonsense, "hum bewakoof the" (I was stupid-in Hindi) now I've become a sensible man.

00:48:45.710 --> 00:48:50.810
You see, actually this Kundalini changes, really transforms you.

00:48:50.810 --> 00:48:51.110


00:48:51.630 --> 00:48:54.690
Now they say that we have six enemies, kaam, krodh, mad matsar, lobh, moh,

