only six they are saying but nowadays

00:49:00.690 --> 00:49:02.950
I think there are more but as it is

00:49:02.950 --> 00:49:04.610
accepted as six of them.

00:49:05.110 --> 00:49:08.370
So once you get connected with this Divine

00:49:08.370 --> 00:49:12.210
power of love, all these things just drop out,

00:49:12.210 --> 00:49:17.390
