00:49:18.050 --> 00:49:18.290


00:49:18.970 --> 00:49:21.390
We have many people also in the foreign

00:49:21.390 --> 00:49:24.330
service and they told us that people are

00:49:24.330 --> 00:49:25.890
very happy with us, I said, Why?

00:49:26.630 --> 00:49:29.210
Because we are not competitive, they are all

00:49:29.210 --> 00:49:33.110
