You don't hanker after people, you don't hanker after people,

00:50:07.010 --> 00:50:12.550
you don't hanker after great publicity or anything, you just

00:50:12.550 --> 00:50:17.030
automatically become so balanced and you are not bothered

00:50:17.030 --> 00:50:20.430
