way people used to discuss and talk about

00:51:32.430 --> 00:51:33.850
things, you know, and I used to keep

00:51:33.850 --> 00:51:36.070
quiet so they thought, I don't even know

00:51:36.070 --> 00:51:38.970
English or maybe I'm so quiet because perhaps,

00:51:39.130 --> 00:51:40.750
maybe I'm good for nothing.

00:51:40.870 --> 00:51:45.110
Possible but now all the same persons, those

00:51:45.110 --> 00:51:49.550
same ladies and gentlemen are now doing meditation,

00:51:50.250 --> 00:51:55.050
now for meditation you don't have to hang

00:51:55.050 --> 00:51:58.010
yourself with anything, you don't have to have

00:51:58.010 --> 00:52:02.210
too much time even ten minutes before sleeping

00:52:02.210 --> 00:52:06.310
you do meditation, you'll feel so relaxed and

00:52:06.310 --> 00:52:15.230
so very absolutely completely cleared out of your

00:52:15.230 --> 00:52:19.110
problems, cleared out of your thinking, just relax.

00:52:20.050 --> 00:52:24.350
There's no thinking which is thoughtless awareness, has

00:52:24.350 --> 00:52:26.670
been already told to us by Jung.

00:52:27.110 --> 00:52:28.830
You know Jung, who was a disciple of

00:52:28.830 --> 00:52:32.070
Freud, whom he revolted against and he talked

00:52:32.070 --> 00:52:33.390
about the Mother Energy.

00:52:34.130 --> 00:52:37.530
We Indians, you see, are Shakti pujaris, nowadays there's

00:52:37.530 --> 00:52:40.210
school, there's Navratras are going on but

00:52:40.210 --> 00:52:44.790
we have never understood the message of Mother's love.

00:52:46.270 --> 00:52:50.930
It is the Mother's love that works,

00:52:50.930 --> 00:52:55.270
I think and you also become very motherly, very kind,

00:52:55.270 --> 00:52:57.270
very compassionate.

00:52:58.090 --> 00:53:00.870
How can a human being, I don't know

00:53:00.870 --> 00:53:04.870
how can he be cruel to anyone who

00:53:04.870 --> 00:53:09.350
is suffering, who is in trouble, who is

00:53:09.350 --> 00:53:12.750
in poverty the love that you have within

00:53:12.750 --> 00:53:17.170
yourself starts flowing just like an ocean and

00:53:17.170 --> 00:53:20.810
you become extremely generous and all the generous

00:53:20.810 --> 00:53:24.850
people I've seen are very much always looked after.

00:53:24.850 --> 00:53:25.150


00:53:26.630 --> 00:53:28.910
I'll give an example of My father,

00:53:28.910 --> 00:53:31.650
who was a very generous man, very, very generous

00:53:32.710 --> 00:53:35.270
and once what happened, he always used to

00:53:35.270 --> 00:53:37.870
say, never close the houses, we should not

00:53:37.870 --> 00:53:41.310
close our house always open the windows, open the doors.

00:53:41.310 --> 00:53:41.850


00:53:43.550 --> 00:53:45.950
He said, something, if you tell him the

00:53:45.950 --> 00:53:47.430
thieves might come he said, let them come.

00:53:47.590 --> 00:53:49.730
After all they need something but that's why they are coming.

00:53:49.730 --> 00:53:50.130


00:53:50.650 --> 00:53:52.610
So he used to keep all the doors open.

00:53:52.610 --> 00:53:52.770


00:53:53.410 --> 00:53:55.230
He had a big, he was fond of music

00:53:55.230 --> 00:53:57.610
so had a big gramophone with

00:53:57.610 --> 00:54:02.210
a one big horn like thing and one day

00:54:02.210 --> 00:54:04.830
one thief came, opened the door,

00:54:04.830 --> 00:54:07.630
it was open, door was open only, he took away that gramophone.

00:54:07.630 --> 00:54:08.290


00:54:09.170 --> 00:54:11.550
So next day he was sitting very seriously.

00:54:12.490 --> 00:54:14.370
So My mother said, Now are you sorry for that?

00:54:14.370 --> 00:54:14.810


00:54:14.910 --> 00:54:16.950
No, no, no that I can buy but

00:54:16.950 --> 00:54:19.650
I'm only sorry, this man seems to be

00:54:19.650 --> 00:54:22.850
connoisseur of music, he's taken away the gramophone.

00:54:23.510 --> 00:54:24.590
Now what will he play?

00:54:24.750 --> 00:54:26.450
He has not taken any records.

00:54:27.770 --> 00:54:30.810
So My mother said, All right, you advertise in the newspaper.

00:54:30.810 --> 00:54:31.530


00:54:32.330 --> 00:54:35.090
The one who has taken the gramophone should

00:54:35.090 --> 00:54:38.750
please come and take the records so that

00:54:38.750 --> 00:54:40.610
he enjoys the gramophone.

00:54:40.910 --> 00:54:44.090
I mean, I've seen such people, I've seen

00:54:44.090 --> 00:54:47.810
very, very generous people and at the time

00:54:47.810 --> 00:54:51.670
when Gandhiji declared the war of independence,

00:54:51.670 --> 00:54:54.130
they not only went to jail but they gave

00:54:54.130 --> 00:54:56.550
away everything that they had.

00:54:57.370 --> 00:54:59.530
We used to live in huge big houses

00:54:59.530 --> 00:55:02.890
then we shifted to some sort of huts

00:55:02.890 --> 00:55:06.810
and we're enjoying because you see, the enjoyment

00:55:06.810 --> 00:55:11.930
was of our Rashtra Bhakti and this has helped.

00:55:11.930 --> 00:55:12.430


00:55:13.190 --> 00:55:17.010
That time Mahatma Gandhi was helped because

00:55:17.010 --> 00:55:18.690
that time the people were like that.

00:55:19.110 --> 00:55:21.850
Now today the thing is, it's coming from the West.

00:55:21.850 --> 00:55:22.430


00:55:23.150 --> 00:55:25.510
Too much of this, too much of that

00:55:26.310 --> 00:55:29.210
It's all right, there's nothing wrong, nothing wrong.

00:55:29.870 --> 00:55:32.170
It should come, we should prosper, our country

00:55:32.170 --> 00:55:35.750
should prosper, we should create more things,

00:55:35.750 --> 00:55:39.330
I agree there but this hankering will go away.

00:55:40.330 --> 00:55:42.790
Now the hankering becomes the other way round.

00:55:43.410 --> 00:55:46.350
Like, what should I give to this lady,

00:55:47.190 --> 00:55:49.210
what should I do for this gentleman?

00:55:49.550 --> 00:55:51.110
I mean, the worry goes to the other side only.

00:55:51.110 --> 00:55:51.790


00:55:52.350 --> 00:55:55.110
See, what to do, what should I give

00:55:55.110 --> 00:55:58.130
that they won't feel right because sometimes you know,

00:55:58.130 --> 00:56:01.310
Sarkari Naukar, as they are very strict

00:56:01.830 --> 00:56:03.370
so if you give them, they think

00:56:03.370 --> 00:56:04.150
I'll give them a bribe.

00:56:04.350 --> 00:56:06.330
I said, it's not a bribe, I'm just

00:56:06.330 --> 00:56:07.910
giving because I want to give you so will you take it?

00:56:07.910 --> 00:56:08.570


00:56:08.990 --> 00:56:11.950
With very great difficulty they'll take but you

00:56:11.950 --> 00:56:15.010
see, is a way of expression of your love

00:56:15.010 --> 00:56:18.510
and with this love I tell you,

00:56:19.570 --> 00:56:23.830
you will be so very popular, so very

00:56:23.830 --> 00:56:29.050
popular in your office, in your work,

00:56:29.050 --> 00:56:32.270
in the whole of the country people will remember

00:56:32.270 --> 00:56:34.890
it that this was the man who really

00:56:34.890 --> 00:56:37.190
looked after us, who has done so much for us.

00:56:37.190 --> 00:56:37.530


00:56:37.890 --> 00:56:40.890
If you don't have a concern you will

00:56:40.890 --> 00:56:43.490
be just worried about yourself and this thing.

00:56:44.250 --> 00:56:45.990
All the ladies also of the IAS,

00:56:45.990 --> 00:56:48.530
thank you very much for inviting Me but

00:56:48.530 --> 00:56:50.870
I would like to tell you that ladies have to help the husband.

00:56:50.870 --> 00:56:51.690


00:56:52.410 --> 00:56:55.790
They should try to understand that their energy

00:56:55.790 --> 00:56:59.410
is the Shakti's energy and they should give

00:56:59.410 --> 00:57:02.690
to men this energy so that they can work better.

00:57:02.690 --> 00:57:03.510


00:57:04.310 --> 00:57:08.270
But sometimes I have funny experiences which I'll

00:57:08.270 --> 00:57:09.970
relate to you which was very interesting.

00:57:10.590 --> 00:57:13.190
That first time, first of all,

00:57:13.190 --> 00:57:16.330
I never know your seniority, juniority, anything I don't

00:57:16.330 --> 00:57:18.010
know much I don't understand.

00:57:18.470 --> 00:57:20.930
I came to Delhi and when My husband

00:57:20.930 --> 00:57:24.330
came here to work for Shastriji so we met

00:57:24.330 --> 00:57:26.150
in a party a friend of Mine

00:57:26.150 --> 00:57:28.830
who was from My college.

00:57:30.550 --> 00:57:33.510
So she asked Me, Arey, how are you here, Nirmala?

00:57:33.510 --> 00:57:34.050


00:57:34.430 --> 00:57:36.450
I said, My husband has come here.

00:57:36.930 --> 00:57:37.850
She said, What is he doing?

00:57:38.170 --> 00:57:40.790
I said, He is a government servant.

00:57:41.150 --> 00:57:43.170
Everybody is a government servant here but what he's doing?

00:57:43.170 --> 00:57:43.490


00:57:43.610 --> 00:57:44.830
I said, I don't know that but he's something here.

00:57:44.830 --> 00:57:45.490


00:57:45.990 --> 00:57:46.670
Where do you live?

00:57:46.790 --> 00:57:47.610
First thing she asked.

00:57:48.050 --> 00:57:49.950
I said, I live in Meena Bagh.

00:57:50.290 --> 00:57:53.850
Ah, Meena Bagh, what is your husband doing?

00:57:54.170 --> 00:57:55.850
You could have got a much better husband.

00:57:56.230 --> 00:57:58.590
Why did you marry a man who takes you to Meena Bagh?

00:57:58.590 --> 00:57:59.270


00:58:00.050 --> 00:58:01.950
Baba, I didn't know Meena Bagh was that bad, you see.

00:58:02.550 --> 00:58:02.930


00:58:03.450 --> 00:58:06.950
because Shastriji, you see, asked us to

00:58:06.950 --> 00:58:09.150
come here and there was no house

00:58:09.150 --> 00:58:10.430
so they gave us Meena Bagh.

00:58:11.390 --> 00:58:13.390
I thought this was very bad to live

00:58:13.390 --> 00:58:14.970
in Meena Bagh the way she was talking.

00:58:15.850 --> 00:58:18.190
Then she said, All right, this gentleman who

00:58:18.190 --> 00:58:21.030
is coming, this tall gentleman, you know, he's very,

00:58:21.030 --> 00:58:22.170
very important.

00:58:22.690 --> 00:58:24.830
You somehow or other manage to talk to

00:58:24.830 --> 00:58:27.390
him, he'll get your husband a very good job

00:58:27.390 --> 00:58:29.230
and you'll get a very good house.

00:58:30.050 --> 00:58:32.370
And who comes there was My husband.

00:58:33.010 --> 00:58:33.990
Oh My God!

00:58:34.790 --> 00:58:36.070
She said, You know him?

00:58:36.390 --> 00:58:37.030
I said, Yes.
How?

00:58:37.590 --> 00:58:37.850


00:58:38.230 --> 00:58:38.950
He's My husband.

00:58:39.390 --> 00:58:40.890
After that she didn't come.

00:58:43.230 --> 00:58:44.770
She never said it to Me.

00:58:45.130 --> 00:58:47.430
To know that they live in Meena Bagh with

00:58:47.430 --> 00:58:49.550
a bad thing itself is a quite

00:58:49.550 --> 00:58:51.370
a big knowledge about things, isn't it?

00:58:51.890 --> 00:58:54.270
That only people of this much pay live

00:58:54.270 --> 00:58:56.150
in Meena Bagh, they live and I mean, it's

00:58:56.150 --> 00:58:57.150
really impossible.

00:58:57.650 --> 00:58:59.450
Even, I mean, don't know, a state officer

00:58:59.450 --> 00:59:02.690
knows this much but the lady knew that

00:59:02.690 --> 00:59:06.430
Meena Bagh was not meant for an IAS office.

00:59:07.010 --> 00:59:08.190
Can you imagine?

00:59:08.850 --> 00:59:12.050
So, these indulgences of the women is of no use.

00:59:12.050 --> 00:59:12.350


00:59:12.390 --> 00:59:14.950
I'm very happy to hear about this organization

00:59:15.850 --> 00:59:17.970
that it is doing such a good constructive work.

00:59:17.970 --> 00:59:18.350


00:59:19.310 --> 00:59:20.690
I was really very happy and

00:59:21.390 --> 00:59:26.690
Myself, he says, I'm a socialist because I always think of the social problems,

00:59:26.830 --> 00:59:28.270
and some or other,

00:59:28.430 --> 00:59:30.570
I'm a socialist, all right, because it's a

00:59:30.570 --> 00:59:34.370
collective sense and when I heard that these

00:59:34.370 --> 00:59:36.630
people are doing this kind of work,

00:59:36.630 --> 00:59:37.510
I said, Amazing!

00:59:38.090 --> 00:59:41.490
I can't imagine those days women used to talk

00:59:41.490 --> 00:59:42.610
of something else.

00:59:43.030 --> 00:59:45.510
They would never talk of any social.

00:59:45.970 --> 00:59:48.990
It was so difficult to make them understand social.

00:59:48.990 --> 00:59:49.450


00:59:49.910 --> 00:59:56.690
Funny type of atmosphere was there the Britishers

00:59:56.690 --> 01:00:00.910
had left their legacy on our heads and

01:00:00.910 --> 01:00:03.750
we were quite enamored by them.

01:00:05.910 --> 01:00:10.710
For example, I would say that it was

01:00:10.710 --> 01:00:15.450
not for them to conceive of something higher or better.

01:00:15.450 --> 01:00:16.090


01:00:16.790 --> 01:00:20.050
So, I was the President of the Blind,

01:00:20.710 --> 01:00:26.690
Friends of the Blind Society and for

01:00:26.690 --> 01:00:29.030
that they were going to have a program

01:00:29.030 --> 01:00:32.450
and these blind were going to act and

01:00:32.450 --> 01:00:34.930
the governor, Mr. Chariot, was to come.

01:00:35.850 --> 01:00:39.390
When he came, they wanted to know who will be

01:00:39.390 --> 01:00:40.670
sitting next to him.

01:00:41.090 --> 01:00:43.190
Being a chairman, of course, they would ask Me to sit down.

01:00:43.190 --> 01:00:43.970


01:00:44.470 --> 01:00:47.550
The rest started quarreling and fighting and discussing

01:00:47.550 --> 01:00:48.970
so much I got such a fright.

01:00:49.570 --> 01:00:51.570
I thought now take to humor, that's the

01:00:51.570 --> 01:00:52.810
best way to solve the problem.

01:00:53.530 --> 01:00:56.390
So, I said, All right, we'll get

01:00:56.390 --> 01:00:59.810
a big plank on top of the governor's head

01:00:59.810 --> 01:01:02.450
and we all sit like sparrows on that.

01:01:03.150 --> 01:01:07.370
Immediately all their anger vanished and we became all right.

01:01:07.370 --> 01:01:07.870


01:01:08.550 --> 01:01:10.770
So, what I'm saying to you, now the

01:01:10.770 --> 01:01:12.990
quality of women have changed.

01:01:13.750 --> 01:01:16.590
You can see that very clearly the quality

01:01:16.590 --> 01:01:21.010
has changed and though, you might think

01:01:21.010 --> 01:01:23.870
that they are rather self-centered or whatever

01:01:23.870 --> 01:01:27.050
you may think but one thing I've noticed

01:01:27.050 --> 01:01:28.910
that they are social minded.

01:01:29.390 --> 01:01:32.490
They read, they understand what's going on in this country.

01:01:32.490 --> 01:01:32.930


01:01:33.610 --> 01:01:36.350
I would say these days our country is

01:01:36.350 --> 01:01:41.150
a very big turmoil, very big turmoil and

01:01:41.150 --> 01:01:47.390
all these things are going to help us

01:01:47.390 --> 01:01:50.430
to solve this problem.

01:01:51.590 --> 01:01:53.730
So many problems we can solve.

01:01:55.290 --> 01:02:01.170
Once some of these problems are solved, I'm sure

01:02:01.170 --> 01:02:03.770
we'll be one of the greatest countries.

01:02:04.230 --> 01:02:07.770
We have no dearth of talent, no doubt.

01:02:08.930 --> 01:02:12.330
We have no dearth of hard work.

01:02:14.310 --> 01:02:18.950
Only "ujaskat tatra durlabha" means that is no one

01:02:18.950 --> 01:02:22.230
is difficult to get a person who can put

01:02:22.230 --> 01:02:27.710
them to the yojana and if such a

01:02:27.710 --> 01:02:30.490
person gets his Self-realization, he's so

01:02:30.490 --> 01:02:34.090
self-confident, so peaceful within himself, he's not bothered

01:02:34.090 --> 01:02:36.610
as to what others are doing and

01:02:36.610 --> 01:02:40.990
all this can change, transform you into a beautiful personality.

01:02:40.990 --> 01:02:41.630


01:02:42.410 --> 01:02:45.590
You give up all your destructive habits, absolutely.

01:02:46.110 --> 01:02:47.810
You just give up your destructive habits.

01:02:48.350 --> 01:02:50.150
I don't have to say, give up, I never say.

01:02:50.150 --> 01:02:50.690


01:02:51.170 --> 01:02:53.410
If I say that half of people might

01:02:53.410 --> 01:02:56.410
leave Me but I've seen people overnight,

01:02:57.130 --> 01:02:59.830
in London there were twelve people who had

01:02:59.830 --> 01:03:02.330
come who were taking drugs, they were drug

01:03:02.330 --> 01:03:05.930
addicts, they left their drugs overnight, overnight.
Can you imagine?

01:03:06.090 --> 01:03:06.590


01:03:06.930 --> 01:03:09.950
I was amazed how could they leave it overnight.

01:03:09.950 --> 01:03:10.490


01:03:11.090 --> 01:03:14.150
Our problems of drugs, of all other things,

01:03:14.490 --> 01:03:17.990
we can solve them without any difficulty and

01:03:17.990 --> 01:03:20.650
you are placed, you are placed for that,

01:03:20.930 --> 01:03:22.890
for that kind of a job.

01:03:22.890 --> 01:03:26.590
Your situation is very good because you have

01:03:26.590 --> 01:03:31.950
a responsibility, very great responsibility and that responsibility

01:03:31.950 --> 01:03:33.570
has to be understood.

01:03:34.330 --> 01:03:37.570
If we do not understand our responsibility, we'll

01:03:37.570 --> 01:03:39.550
not achieve it but once you get your

01:03:39.550 --> 01:03:43.810
realization, you will, you will become extremely responsible

01:03:43.810 --> 01:03:48.090
and also you'll not feel that responsibility on

01:03:48.090 --> 01:03:53.650
your head, you'll feel extremely, absolutely relaxed and

01:03:53.650 --> 01:03:55.890
such a person to meet, you are sometimes surprised.

01:03:55.890 --> 01:03:56.450


01:03:56.870 --> 01:04:00.730
The face changes, the body changes, everything,

01:04:00.730 --> 01:04:03.630
the transformation takes place and you are surprised.

01:04:04.110 --> 01:04:07.230
All this, all this is within you, all

01:04:07.230 --> 01:04:10.510
this you have got it, all this is working out within you.

01:04:10.510 --> 01:04:11.110


01:04:11.350 --> 01:04:15.150
Only thing we have to get our Self-realization.

01:04:15.150 --> 01:04:15.630


01:04:16.570 --> 01:04:20.210
This is a knowledge of our inner being,

01:04:20.510 --> 01:04:21.590
a very subtle knowledge.

01:04:23.750 --> 01:04:27.950
I pray and thank you very much all

01:04:27.950 --> 01:04:30.970
the ladies also for calling Me here.

01:04:31.050 --> 01:04:33.710
This is a very unique experience I have

01:04:33.710 --> 01:04:37.690
because I've never known that IS people could

01:04:37.690 --> 01:04:40.710
be so receptive to this kind of

01:04:40.710 --> 01:04:42.890
a subtle thing but they are.

01:04:43.150 --> 01:04:45.510
In Bombay I was surprised when I had

01:04:45.510 --> 01:04:48.890
this program in Bombay, now they're regularly going

01:04:48.890 --> 01:04:52.170
for meditation in a hall that they have.

01:04:52.690 --> 01:04:55.190
Surprised, how can they do it, I don't

01:04:55.190 --> 01:04:56.710
know but they are doing.

01:04:58.030 --> 01:05:00.690
The way they have received Me, actually

01:05:00.690 --> 01:05:03.550
I used to always say that the Bombay IS

01:05:03.550 --> 01:05:09.370
people are very, very proud, I should say, very proud.

01:05:09.430 --> 01:05:09.970


01:05:10.550 --> 01:05:12.390
They wouldn't look at you, they wouldn't see you

01:05:12.390 --> 01:05:14.830
but I was surprised they have become

01:05:14.830 --> 01:05:16.950
so humble, so nice.

01:05:19.170 --> 01:05:21.510
I don't know why in Bombay they have

01:05:21.510 --> 01:05:24.930
developed this kind of a superiority complex or

01:05:24.930 --> 01:05:29.210
something we had very bad reports about them

01:05:29.210 --> 01:05:32.930
but suddenly they have changed so much and

01:05:32.930 --> 01:05:34.990
in the same way you all should change

01:05:34.990 --> 01:05:37.050
and you become so collective.

01:05:37.910 --> 01:05:41.130
It's not joint, it's collective and you just

01:05:41.130 --> 01:05:44.490
think of helping each other and living that

01:05:44.490 --> 01:05:46.690
kind of a life and all over

01:05:46.690 --> 01:05:49.990
the world we have brothers and sisters.

01:05:50.170 --> 01:05:53.350
Wherever you go, you may go anywhere, you'll find

