You don't have to convince, you see, there's no

01:23:15.280 --> 01:23:18.420
need to convince, because they'll see you

01:23:18.420 --> 01:23:23.060
as something special, very different, and they will

01:23:23.060 --> 01:23:28.780
ask you, how are you so peaceful, how are you

01:23:28.780 --> 01:23:29.700
so good?

01:23:29.700 --> 01:23:34.620
Don't have to tell them, just, they will

01:23:34.620 --> 01:23:37.580
see your character, your style, and they'll be

01:23:37.580 --> 01:23:39.900
so impressed by you.

01:23:43.340 --> 01:23:45.340
Uska wo loudspeaker hi theek nahin kya kare,
(his loudspeaker is not working, what to do)

01:23:45.420 --> 01:23:53.100
aataan ki prashna hai (now, the question is),
very positive questions,

01:23:53.100 --> 01:23:58.780
they are very, very positive, because once you get it,

01:23:58.780 --> 01:24:00.500
you want others to get it also,

01:24:00.500 --> 01:24:03.240
because you find others are in trouble.

